- Wrap up your business with her.

25:52.075 --> 25:53.802
We don't need any noise
around us right now.

25:54.141 --> 25:55.295
What about his brother?

25:55.357 --> 25:57.075
Leave them all alone.

26:02.374 --> 26:03.638
Buckingham Gate.

26:05.469 --> 26:08.208
One of the poorest street
in London back in the day.

26:10.287 --> 26:13.478
Now, it's money for generations.

26:13.598 --> 26:15.201
For the lucky few.

26:16.956 --> 26:18.139
For us.

