29:25.676 --> 29:27.107
You like a bit of fun, don't you?

29:27.120 --> 29:28.653
What else did you do?

29:30.665 --> 29:32.531
- Did you...
- Oh, I didn't touch you

29:32.583 --> 29:34.014
if that's what you're accusing me of.

29:34.667 --> 29:35.936
I'd never do that.

29:36.312 --> 29:38.793
- I'm your mate.
