29:38.817 --> 29:41.598
- that's not how mates behave.
- It's just business.

29:42.877 --> 29:44.490
You've never needed money, have you?

29:45.687 --> 29:47.604
- For me it's everyday!
- I want you to delete

29:47.633 --> 29:49.937
- the photos.
- Nobody else ever had to see them.

29:53.066 --> 29:54.802
But I need you to come to The Mason's Arms,

29:54.826 --> 29:56.538
on Templeton Road at 6.

29:57.416 --> 29:58.175
Why?

29:59.244 --> 30:00.837
There's a bloke I want you to meet.

30:05.864 --> 30:07.061
The first time's tricky.

30:07.367 --> 30:09.528
But swear down, it's not so bad.

30:10.172 --> 30:12.562
The people I work with,
they know how to behave.

30:13.688 --> 30:14.885
I really liked you.

30:15.005 --> 30:17.008
And I like you, you're a nice kid.

30:17.842 --> 30:19.450
But if you're not there at 6,

30:19.956 --> 30:21.363
these go online.

30:40.511 --> 30:41.331
Hey.

30:41.720 --> 30:42.638
You as well.

30:42.758 --> 30:44.055
It's my lucky day.

30:44.679 --> 30:45.657
Two minutes?

30:45.924 --> 30:47.250
I've got a train to catch.

30:47.560 --> 30:48.424
Please.

30:49.907 --> 30:51.076
The clock's running.

30:56.532 --> 30:58.703
I'm sorry you had to go
through this with Julie.

30:59.556 --> 31:00.878
I would have warned you

31:01.321 --> 31:02.657
but I had no idea.

31:06.467 --> 31:07.321
Turn around.

31:08.318 --> 31:09.253
Come on.

31:09.969 --> 31:11.028
Turn around.

31:17.983 --> 31:19.567
I knew what I was doing.

31:20.845 --> 31:22.601
Well, it was my responsibility.

31:23.092 --> 31:24.829
Don't patronize me.

31:26.508 --> 31:28.010
There's no drama here.

31:28.244 --> 31:29.407
We had a laugh,

31:29.474 --> 31:30.800
played like it was real.

31:32.738 --> 31:35.643
You were a few hours of my
week, not a big part of my life.

31:39.378 --> 31:40.719
I cared for you.

31:41.792 --> 31:43.514
Me too. But...

31:44.372 --> 31:45.459
So what?

31:46.575 --> 31:48.693
In the bigger picture, so what?

31:49.233 --> 31:50.888
It wasn't going anywhere.

31:51.809 --> 31:52.844
It was...

31:54.709 --> 31:55.682
fun.

31:58.511 --> 31:59.756
Time's up.

32:02.760 --> 32:03.772
Where are you going?

32:05.094 --> 32:06.935
My mom died last week.

32:08.519 --> 32:09.468
Oh, that's...

32:09.588 --> 32:10.680
Shit.

32:11.320 --> 32:12.382
I'm so sorry.

32:13.059 --> 32:15.234
We bury her on Tuesday.

32:16.813 --> 32:18.139
Anything I can do?

32:19.824 --> 32:20.916
No, thanks.

33:48.627 --> 33:49.786
What do you want?

33:54.856 --> 33:56.111
Have you told him?

33:57.303 --> 33:58.710
He adores you.

33:59.940 --> 34:01.414
He won't thank you for it.

34:01.743 --> 34:03.384
You're only bringing him unhappiness.

34:03.398 --> 34:04.853
He values loyalty.

34:05.617 --> 34:07.038
I could be useful to you.

34:09.308 --> 34:10.811
You got nothing I want.

34:13.473 --> 34:15.987
He'd like you to wear the
black dress for him tonight.

34:17.012 --> 34:20.380
You've come all this way to deliver
a message about a black dress?

34:20.920 --> 34:22.127
That's his message.

34:26.835 --> 34:28.199
You've already told him.

34:30.322 --> 34:31.721
You've killed us.

34:51.496 --> 34:53.648
It's home study. Check with school.

34:54.478 --> 34:55.800
Well then why aren't you at home?

34:57.803 --> 34:58.809
What?

35:00.980 --> 35:03.045
Come on, honey, I've got a
client coming in a minute.

35:03.651 --> 35:05.168
How many clients have you got?

35:06.103 --> 35:07.186
Some.

35:07.978 --> 35:10.019
It's a start-up, takes time.

35:10.539 --> 35:13.135
Like Orla's mom training
to be a yoga teacher.

35:14.060 --> 35:15.243
Aisha's mom a writer.

35:15.258 --> 35:18.101
I'm not even sure if they're real
jobs. They're just rich and bored.

35:18.597 --> 35:20.133
Well, I am neither.

35:21.569 --> 35:22.752
What's going on?

35:24.145 --> 35:25.752
I went to a party last night.

35:26.498 --> 35:28.167
Well, I'm not an idiot.

35:28.181 --> 35:29.884
I knew you weren't to Orla's.

35:30.614 --> 35:31.817
Were you even with her?

35:35.585 --> 35:37.366
Why does everyone keep lying to me?

35:37.390 --> 35:40.566
It is very very hard not
to take it personally!

35:44.040 --> 35:46.634
I'm sorry, I've had a
horrible horrible day.

35:48.771 --> 35:49.682
Maddy.

35:52.993 --> 35:54.958
Ugh, Maddy, come on!

37:02.311 --> 37:05.060
- Oh, hi Michael.
- Hi.

37:05.312 --> 37:07.641
- Good to see you.
- You too.

37:08.656 --> 37:10.240
Come in.

37:19.977 --> 37:22.371
So, the pieces are through here.

37:27.272 --> 37:30.080
I've tried to keep the
lines as simple as possible.

37:30.095 --> 37:33.804
I mean, Hepplewhite to Ercol,
the fundamentals stay the same.

37:35.257 --> 37:36.980
It's beautiful.

37:39.347 --> 37:42.832
- That's like a single piece of wood.
- That was the intention.

37:44.798 --> 37:47.388
So, the other pieces will be be
finished in another day or so.

37:47.407 --> 37:49.000
Where would you like them delivered?

37:49.798 --> 37:51.251
I'll have someone collect them.

37:51.765 --> 37:52.809
OK.

37:56.920 --> 37:58.717
So I suppose this is goodbye.

38:01.452 --> 38:03.158
It's been a pleasure.

38:06.422 --> 38:07.786
Your hands...

38:08.748 --> 38:10.119
they're so soft.

38:10.984 --> 38:12.817
No callouses.

38:12.937 --> 38:15.612
- Well, give it time.
- Have dinner with me.

38:18.578 --> 38:20.099
You know I really am flattered.

38:20.144 --> 38:22.477
- I-I really am.
- Just a goodbye dinner.

38:23.968 --> 38:25.369
Nothing else.

38:28.424 --> 38:31.272
I'm s... I'm so sorry,
just let me deal with this.

38:34.060 --> 38:35.431
Yeah, what is it?

38:36.579 --> 38:39.280
- There's a guy up there with you.
- I'm with a client.

38:39.322 --> 38:41.933
- Get out of there now.
- This really isn't a good time.

38:42.000 --> 38:45.081
I swear to God, get the
fuck out of there now!

38:45.446 --> 38:46.794
Is everything all right?

38:47.288 --> 38:48.248
Yeah.

38:50.320 --> 38:52.989
- I think you're mistaken.
- Julie, listen.

38:53.734 --> 38:56.447
That guy is a killer.
He's Nelson Clay's brother.

38:56.480 --> 38:59.643
You put the phone down, and
get the fuck outta there.

39:02.892 --> 39:03.864
OK.

39:05.975 --> 39:08.282
Yeah, no, I'll deal
with this straight away.

39:08.813 --> 39:10.011
Thanks.

39:15.598 --> 39:18.699
I'm so sorry. I have to go,
there's a... a family emergency.

39:20.517 --> 39:22.289
- Nothing serious I hope.
- Oh, no.

39:22.324 --> 39:24.947
Not at all. Just, you
know, stuff with the kids.

39:25.448 --> 39:27.309
I will see you tonight?

39:28.244 --> 39:29.181
Yeah?

39:31.530 --> 39:32.759
8 o'clock?

39:33.259 --> 39:34.643
Of course.

39:36.449 --> 39:37.772
Yeah, I'll call you.

39:44.760 --> 39:45.976
After you.

40:01.699 --> 40:02.880
I'll see you tonight.

40:02.909 --> 40:04.108
Sure.

40:05.414 --> 40:07.525
Thanks for everything, Michael. Bye.

40:12.593 --> 40:15.134
- Come on.
- No, I am fine on my own!

40:15.160 --> 40:17.131
He knows who you are. His name is Victor.

40:17.149 --> 40:20.280
- He's very sick, very dangerous.
- What? I thought he was client?

40:20.400 --> 40:22.783
- You need protection.
- What? From them?

40:22.825 --> 40:24.429
Or from you and my husband?

40:24.677 --> 40:26.776
- Wait, wait, wait!
- You know what? Get off me!

40:27.241 --> 40:29.441
- Did he tell you his wife died?
- Yes!

40:29.829 --> 40:31.535
Did he tell you that he killed her

40:31.655 --> 40:33.789
and fucked her dead body for a week?

40:33.807 --> 40:35.399
And he did it to other girls too!

40:35.519 --> 40:38.315
- That's who you were kissing right now!
- No! You know, fuck you!

40:38.380 --> 40:41.158
I have done nothing to upset these people!

40:41.278 --> 40:43.418
You know, the more I am
involved with your family,

40:43.430 --> 40:45.088
the more I seem to need protection.

40:45.112 --> 40:46.776
Why is that, do you think?

41:42.272 --> 41:45.468
"Call from Dad"

41:46.810 --> 41:49.869
"Call from Dad"

41:52.372 --> 41:53.487
Where are you?

41:53.511 --> 41:56.529
I'm not angry, I'm just really worried.

41:57.561 --> 41:59.725
Could you please call me straight away?

42:00.888 --> 42:02.104
Please.

42:04.495 --> 42:05.890
Here she is.

42:10.451 --> 42:11.864
Where you been?

42:13.827 --> 42:14.971
Gerry.

42:15.480 --> 42:16.641
This is Maddy.

42:16.969 --> 42:18.842
She's been looking forward to meet you.

42:19.026 --> 42:20.827
Maddy, it's a pleasure.

42:23.934 --> 42:25.336
What would you like to drink?

42:26.022 --> 42:27.363
Do you like vodka?

42:42.097 --> 42:42.926
Hey!

42:43.046 --> 42:43.772
Hey!

42:44.243 --> 42:45.323
Stop!

42:48.698 --> 42:50.468
What did you and Maddy do last night?

42:50.504 --> 42:52.757
- We hung out at mine.
- Don't lie to me!

42:52.877 --> 42:54.469
She said you went to see a film.

42:54.660 --> 42:57.111
- Yeah, that too.
- Stop fucking around!

42:57.552 --> 42:59.031
I can't get a hold of her.

42:59.880 --> 43:00.986
Is she in trouble?

43:02.638 --> 43:03.747
Answer me!

43:04.702 --> 43:06.329
OK, she wasn't with me.

43:06.449 --> 43:07.826
You need to talk to Maddy.

43:07.946 --> 43:09.413
Where did she get this money?

43:09.746 --> 43:11.296
It's nothing to do with me.

43:11.630 --> 43:12.853
Please.

43:16.377 --> 43:17.969
She went to a party.

43:17.993 --> 43:20.360
A friend of mine has got
a flat around the corner.

43:20.563 --> 43:22.191
It's really smart.

43:22.828 --> 43:24.325
I can show you.

43:28.350 --> 43:30.914
- She knows the drill, doesn't she?
- She knows.

43:32.179 --> 43:33.598
Why don't we go now?

43:35.154 --> 43:37.027
I'll just go to the bathroom.

43:39.287 --> 43:41.517
Don't even think of running away.

43:44.993 --> 43:46.526
I'm waiting right here.

43:46.865 --> 43:49.614
If you're not out in two
minutes, I'm coming in.

44:12.903 --> 44:15.294
Dad, please, I've done something stupid.

44:58.291 --> 44:59.686
What are you doing?

45:00.777 --> 45:02.006
Trust me.

45:04.003 --> 45:05.458
I'm your husband.

45:08.940 --> 45:10.317
Don't get spooked.

45:11.641 --> 45:13.644
I'm probably more nervous than you are.

45:14.425 --> 45:16.131
One more drink please.

45:18.354 --> 45:20.304
I've never done this before.

45:26.202 --> 45:28.259
- Get your fucking hands off her!
- Take it easy, friend.

45:28.271 --> 45:29.596
I'm her father.

45:29.631 --> 45:31.366
You're going nowhere.

45:31.486 --> 45:34.448
What's a grown man doing giving
alcohol to a 13-year-old girl?

45:34.466 --> 45:36.041
He's the one who took the pictures.

45:36.065 --> 45:38.109
- Give me your phone.
- Make me an offer.

45:38.110 --> 45:39.666
Don't play games, kid!

45:41.151 --> 45:42.916
The pictures are already out there.

45:43.166 --> 45:46.004
There are people spanking
on them right now.

45:47.459 --> 45:50.208
You better hope not, you sack of shit!

45:50.458 --> 45:52.962
If that's true, I will find you,

45:53.082 --> 45:55.466
and I'll cut your fucking balls off!

45:55.472 --> 45:57.303
Dad, it's enough.

46:07.148 --> 46:08.353
Come on.

46:23.290 --> 46:24.870
Just tell me.

46:25.448 --> 46:27.088
Where are we going?

46:28.775 --> 46:31.142
Well, that would ruin the surprise.

46:58.680 --> 47:00.521
Does Mom know about the pictures?

47:01.976 --> 47:03.747
I've tried to tell her.

47:05.125 --> 47:06.633
Can we keep it to ourselves?

47:07.539 --> 47:08.433
No.

47:09.889 --> 47:12.197
We tell each other the truth, from now.

47:12.680 --> 47:14.141
However painful.

47:19.841 --> 47:21.093
Where did you get the money?

47:25.601 --> 47:27.160
Did they make you do anything?

47:27.169 --> 47:29.221
It's not what you think, I promise.

47:30.062 --> 47:31.886
I sold something, that's all.

47:35.422 --> 47:36.340
OK.

47:39.400 --> 47:40.741
Are you going to work?

47:40.800 --> 47:42.344
No, I...

47:44.600 --> 47:46.203
I can't come in right now.

47:47.163 --> 47:48.880
Things are not great.

47:49.805 --> 47:51.683
Nobody's fault but mine.

47:52.267 --> 47:54.819
I love you, and Oliver, and Mom.

47:56.596 --> 47:58.010
We're gonna be all right.

48:51.637 --> 48:52.520
Hi.

48:52.640 --> 48:54.105
I'm not coming for dinner.

48:54.135 --> 48:55.459
I know who you are.

48:55.870 --> 48:57.120
That's a shame.

48:57.289 --> 48:58.577
What were you doing?

48:58.697 --> 49:00.646
I was enjoying myself.

49:01.511 --> 49:02.911
I didn't have to be me.

49:03.126 --> 49:04.426
Did you like me?

49:06.173 --> 49:07.747
When I was Michael?

49:10.037 --> 49:11.629
I will never see you again.

49:12.034 --> 49:13.686
Well, if that's what you want.

49:17.275 --> 49:18.820
But I will see you.

50:07.726 --> 50:09.509
Take the blindfold off.

50:45.882 --> 50:47.146
It's for you.

50:53.145 --> 50:54.200
You OK?

50:54.320 --> 50:55.804
Where did you think I was taking you?

51:04.600 --> 51:06.760
You're a miserable drinking
companion, you know that?

51:06.805 --> 51:07.997
I fucked up.

51:08.391 --> 51:10.173
That's an understatement.

51:14.400 --> 51:16.400
Sonny was more than a liaison, you know.

51:16.520 --> 51:18.563
Don't compare your

51:19.499 --> 51:22.081
humping in a cupboard to my marriage.

51:22.945 --> 51:25.068
We didn't hump in a cupboard.

51:26.797 --> 51:27.906
We humped

51:28.026 --> 51:29.617
in lots of other places.

51:30.679 --> 51:32.720
And if Victor hadn't found out,

51:33.120 --> 51:35.073
we might have had a chance.

51:37.756 --> 51:39.676
I've been trying to deal with it.

51:40.833 --> 51:42.044
How?

51:47.178 --> 51:48.167
Kill him

51:48.704 --> 51:50.302
before he talks to Nelson.

51:50.725 --> 51:52.812
You'd stroll up,

51:53.653 --> 51:55.299
finish him, and

51:55.651 --> 51:57.142
Nelson would never know?

51:58.024 --> 52:00.582
You know what? Feel free to help, any time.

52:01.360 --> 52:03.355
How come it's all on me? Uh?

52:04.595 --> 52:06.169
It's you Victor hates.

52:14.983 --> 52:16.307
He sent me this.

52:19.883 --> 52:21.713
You're kidding me. He was at the house?

52:23.585 --> 52:25.743
Why does this happen to us?

52:26.913 --> 52:28.642
It's our inheritance.

52:32.118 --> 52:33.728
Victor has to die.

52:34.280 --> 52:36.077
He's a danger to everyone.

52:40.600 --> 52:42.576
- I'll kill him.
- No.

52:45.439 --> 52:47.585
Nelson will kill him for us.

